reviewText: As an Agriculture Teacher, I strive to introduce subjects to my students in non-traditional methods to increase retention and interest. The students in my class liked this video, the fact that it was made by other students and the fact that the subject matter is relevant to today's poultry industry.
very infromative. great for the classroom
Happy with content and a great learning video for our 4H kids and adults . Would be great in classroom too.
